          "Week 6\n{AUC: 0.72 - RF-EnsembleMarras}\n\nWeek 10\n{AUC: 0.77 - RF-EnsembleAll}",
          "The main distinction of this paper is that it keeps the same algorithm and tests multiple distinct feature sets. \n\nAuthors identify that an emsemble of their own feature set is better for early prediction.\n\nAuthors then follow-up with a generalization study over a total of 4 curricular units - 2 FP and 2 MOOCs. \n\nThe feature sets selected in one and the other are different.",
          "Course-specific models"
        ]
