    {
      "id": "95e47a56-5b66-4552-af4a-23bdece5657a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The intent behind early predictors of student success is to help students and the state of the art has evolved considerably with time. The paper does a 2-part split. First, it reviews early predictors and, then, it analyzes 8 feature sets that have been successful in recent years. Then, the authors introduce another feature set. Results are compared using a RF and an analysis of the feature importances is subsequently performed.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "95e47a56-5b66-4552-af4a-23bdece5657a",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
